The tool focuses on resource types and configurations most likely to be affected by subscription transfers:

  Managed Identity (SystemAssigned), User Assigned Identities, Key Vaults, AKS, SQL Databases, ADLS Gen2 Storage, App Services, VMs/Disks/Snapshots (encryption hints), Synapse, Purview,   Databricks, Event Hub, Service Bus, ACR, Logic Apps, Data Factory, Azure ML, Container Apps, Redis, ADX, Private Endpoints, Private DNS.

Queries are intentionally kept portable (no KQL let/dynamic constants; avoided unsupported functions such as array_join).
